io.spine.server.rejection

Interface RejectionDispatcherDelegate<I>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type of IDs of entities to which dispatch rejections
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AggregatePartRepository, AggregateRepository, CommandLifecycleRepository, EntityHistoryRepository, ProcessManagerRepository

    @Internal
public interface RejectionDispatcherDelegate<I>
    A common interface for objects which need to dispatch rejections but are unable to implement RejectionDispatcher.

    This interface defines own contract (instead of extending MessageDispatcher to allow classes that dispatch messages other than rejections (by implementing MessageDispatcher),

    See Also:
    DelegatingRejectionDispatcher
